transcript: Umm Ameena from the Emirates. Assalamu Alaikum. Salam to Allah. So I have a question about my period start after Alaysha. And what the problem is, I knew when Alaysha's time came, like around 7.30. I think I wasn't, the period didn't start, but I didn't get up until like two hours later. Al-Fajr.
